com.tbg.adapter.tbg.marketdatafeed

Class TBGMarketDataFeed

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tbg.core.model.marketDataFeed.BacktestMarketDataFeedBase
      • com.tbg.adapter.tbg.marketdatafeed.TBGMarketDataFeed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMarketDataFeed

    public class TBGMarketDataFeed
extends BacktestMarketDataFeedBase
implements IMarketDataFeed
    TheBonnotGang MarketDataFeed Adapter
    - Loads csv quotes 1minutes candles and generates fake tickEvents by using the CandleToTick class.
    - Gets the quotes from online by conecting to the BonnotGang website
     The Bonnot Gang Csv Format is like the follow:
 
 
 1 column : symbol      ex. GS
 2 column : number      ex. 23
 3 column : date/time   ex. 7/10/2011 15:38
 4 column : open                ex. 96,55
 5 column : high                ex. 96,67
 6 column : low         ex. 96,45
 7 column : close               ex. 96,57
 8 column : volume      ex. 31800
 
 Historical 1 minute candle csv file can be found here: www.thebonnotgang.com
 Free registration is needed to access the Historical Data downloading.
 
 WARNING:
 When you backtest using ESPER time windows, you have to be sure to repeat the candleEvent at the same time 
 of the original by setting the super.SLEEP_TIME accordingly with your csv candles.
 Backtesting this way do not garantee the same results of reality.

    Author:
    sfl Oct,12,2011
